    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood from the species Schinopsis lorentzii. It is extremely hard, polishes well, and has a spotted reddish brown appearance. It is generally stained black. It is used for carvings, railway sleepers, and heavy construction.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
